---
title: Double Plant-Based Crumbed Chick'n & Kumara Fries with Apple Salad & Beetroot Relish
description: A plant-based version of chicken tenders, yes it can be done. A sweet beetroot relish on the side gives us a match we never knew we needed. It’s perfect for dipping the fries in too!

